    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202480/extras/0c1dd53cfb52da990808cfb167a372a4.webp?t=1719052442\" width=32 height=32 /></span><i><strong>随机地牢</strong></i><br><i>由程序生成诸如怪物，资源，路径，地牢出口等内容，都隐藏在迷雾之中等待探索。</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202480/extras/62021fc20cbab53d5529f3be45c13737.webp?t=1719052442\" width=32 height=32 /></span><i><strong>各异怪物</strong></i><br>能力各异的怪物分布在地牢各处阻挡路径或守护宝藏，单独出现时它们或许微不足道，但随机组合在一起也许会变成巨大的威胁。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202480/extras/f421f0b69f6d4caa72ea2260f10142a9.webp?t=1719052442\" width=32 height=32 /></span><i><strong>丰富构筑</strong></i><br>用上百张功能不同的卡牌，配合数十种独特的神器以及玩法各异的职业，构筑你强大的卡组来应付棘手的状况。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202480/extras/d42cd2b07b7a77030bd91f7585f122e9.webp?t=1719052442\" width=32 height=32 /></span><i><strong>打造卡牌</strong></i><br>你的卡牌可以被无限升级，叠加大量词缀，使其变得更加强大且独特。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202480/extras/8f5e1d367750740bea83a9f81a040f56.webp?t=1719052442\" width=32 height=32 /></span><i><strong>跨越限制</strong></i><br>游戏中虽然有职业的概念，且卡牌也存在职业类型，但是它们是通用的，所有职业的卡牌都允许被组合在一起。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202480/extras/9d69b26f36560321bf1a8d080103de0b.webp?t=1719052442\" width=32 height=32 /></span><i><strong>不断进化</strong></i><br>随着不断深入地牢，怪物会进化成更高级的形态，以及获得更多的特殊能力以阻止你继续前进。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202480/extras/033b2e06b681a531408c10063b2365db.webp?t=1719052442\" width=32 height=32 /></span><i><strong>强大BOSS</strong></i><br>地牢每层都会有一个由程序生成的不可预测的精英怪物，它一人成军，你必需打败它才能进入下一层。而且游戏中还存在数个强大的独特领主随时准备着终结你的旅程！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202480/extras/0f7710879c6ec15579ccf9e9343c7dd9.webp?t=1719052442\" width=32 height=32 /></span><i><strong>无限承传</strong></i><br>如果在战斗中不幸被击败，只要你口袋里还有几个金币，就能把你幸苦打造的卡牌继承至下一局游戏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202480/extras/e2f55271dfb340e9aa35f32dad268aec.webp?t=1719052442\" width=32 height=32 /></span><i><strong>环保护肝</strong></i><br>游戏中没有任何需要花费大量时间解锁的强化内容，一切只凭技巧加上一些（或者很多）运气。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2202480/extras/ddec40faa708ce1888162f16c6ec7fcf.webp?t=1719052442\" width=32 height=32 /></span><i><strong>无尽挑战</strong></i><br>游戏目前不存在通关概念，你可以一直带着你的卡组向地牢深处挺进并不断打破纪录。",
